data.description: WALK/BIKE TO UF! Located in the highly sought after area of midtown, this 4/2 on a massive lot is everything you’ve been searching for. Previously used as two 2/1 residences, this could easily be converted back as there are separate entrances for each residence and all plumbing set up to put a kitchen back into the second residence. Thus, the possibilities are endless to either make this home your primary residence, or an incredible investment! Featuring new HVAC’s (2020 & 2021), new hot water heater (2020), newer appliances, matured landscaping, and more! The custom, oversized windows throughout create an exorbitant amount of natural light, and the wooded side lot buffer allows for ultimate privacy. Stepping outside, throw a bbq on your large concrete patio, allow your fur babies to run free in your fully fenced yard, and store an abundance of belongings in your generously sized shed. The concrete block construction and no HOA make for low cost living, all while being centrally situated across from University of Florida. It’s such a rarity for a home of this caliber, for this price, in such a prime location to come on the market. Call today to schedule your showing!
